{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回 要命的婚事\n\n沈璧君在返回沈家庄途中，被假扮连家车夫的小公子手下截获。赶车人与青衣妇人企图劫持沈璧君，彭鹏飞因畏惧小公子而袖手旁观。关键时刻柳永南出手杀死车夫，救下沈璧君。然而彭鹏飞随即揭露柳永南实为采花盗，两人互相揭短后大打出手。沈璧君趁乱驾马车逃走，却不幸撞树。\n\n小公子现身，以残忍手段折磨沈璧君，逼迫她答应\"报答\"柳永南，并安排两人当场成亲。小公子的手段极其阴毒——既让柳永南娶到沈璧君，又让他从此过不上一天太平日子。正当小公子得意之际，萧十一郎鬼魅般出现，以其人之道还治其人之身，反过来要将小公子嫁给柳永南。小公子趁乱暗算柳永南致其重伤，随即施展轻功逃脱，临走留下要嫁给萧十一郎的戏言。萧十一郎虽明知小公子毒如蛇蝎，却偏偏有些不忍下辣手。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为什么一直不肯承认他是我的朋友？难道我真的这么高贵？他又有什么地方不如人？我凭什么要看不起他？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人为了保全自己的名誉和地位，就不惜牺牲别人和伤害别人，我岂非也正和大多数人一样？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "连夫人受惊了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "多谢你关心，这次要劳你的驾了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_fu_ren",
      "text": "快扶夫人上车，今天咱们还要赶好长的路呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然没有备别的车马，就请彭大侠和柳公子一齐上车吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "有小人等护送夫人回庄已经足够，用不着再劳动他们两位了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "是是是，在下也正想告辞。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "这次劳动了两位，我家公子日后一定不会忘了两位的好处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "你家公子是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我家公子……自然是连公子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "连公子？你是连家的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "你若是连家的人，我怎会没有见到过你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有些话夫人还是不问的好，问多了反而自找烦恼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "彭大侠，柳公子，这人究竟是谁？这究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人最好也莫要问他，纵然问了他，他也说不出来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_fu_ren",
      "text": "你们还不快扶夫人上车，还在等什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣妇人",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人还是请安心上车吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "你们竟敢对我无礼？快放手，彭鹏飞，你既是连城璧的朋友，怎能眼看他们如此对待我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "只要夫人见到我们公子，一切事就都会明白的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "你家公子莫非就是那……那……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "彭大侠、柳公子，两位请便吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "好，你……你好大的胆子……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "永南，你……你这祸可真的闯大了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "我真不懂你这么做是何居心？小公子的手段，你又不是不知道。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "那么你……你为什么还要这样做？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "无论如何，我也不能将连夫人送到那班恶魔的手上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "多谢你，柳公子，我……我总算还没有看错你。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人的意思，自然是说看错我了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "其实我又何尝不想救你，但救了你又有什么用呢？你我三人加起来也绝非小公子的敌手，迟早还是要落入他掌握中的！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "原来是他要你们来找我的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "否则我们怎会知道夫人会在山神庙里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，他对你们的疑心并没有错，我反而错怪他了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那人也不是好东西，对夫人也绝不会存着什么好心。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "只有你存的是好心，是么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "只可惜你存的这番好心，我早已看透了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "我虽然知道你素来好色如命，却未想到你的色胆竟有这么大，主意竟打到连夫人身上来了，但你也不想想，这样的天鹅肉，就凭你也能吃得到嘴么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "这只是你以小人之心度君子之腹，柳公子绝不是这样的人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你以为他是好人？告诉你，这些年来，每个月坏在他手上的黄花闺女，没有十个，也有八个。只不过谁也不会想到无恶不作的采花盗，竟会是'芙蓉剑'柳三爷的大少爷而已。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "就因为他有这些把柄被小公子捏在手上，所以才只有乖乖的听话……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "你呢？你又是什么好东西，你若没有把柄被小公子捏在手上，他也就不会找到你了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "我有什么把柄？你说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "现在你固然是大财主了，但你的家财是哪里来的？你以为我不知道？你明里虽是在开镖局，其实却比强盗还狠，谁托你保镖，那真是倒了八辈子楣，卸任的张知府要你护送回乡，你在半路上就把人家一家大小十八口杀得干干净净，你以为你做的这些事真没人知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "放你妈的屁，你这小畜生……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你这小杂种色胆包天，我可犯不上陪你送死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "你想怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "彭鹏飞",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你若乖乖的随我去见小公子，我也许还会替你说两句好话，饶你不死！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_peng_peng_fei",
      "text": "你这是在做梦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "站住！你若敢再往前走一步，我就死在这里！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你放心，只管往前走就是，我敢担保她绝不会死的，她若真的想死，也就不会活到现在了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好姑娘，你想死也死不了，还是好好的活着吧，你若觉得一个人太孤单，我就找个人来陪你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我跟你有什么冤仇？你为何连死都不让我死！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "就因为我们一点冤仇都没有，所以我才舍不得让你死。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "过来呀，站在那里干什么？这么大的人，难道还害臊么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "看你多不小心，好好的一张脸竟被人打肿了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "嗯，这样才总算勉强可以见人了，但下次还是要小心些，宁可被人打屁股，也莫要被人打到脸，知道么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这位柳家的大少爷，你认得吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "张开眼睛来，听我说话，我问一句，你就答一句，知道吗？你若不听话，我就只好剥光你的衣服……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "对了，这才是乖孩子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这位柳家的大少爷，方才杀了四个人，连他的好朋友彭鹏飞都被他杀了，你知道他是为了什么吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "摇头不可以，要说话。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我……我不知道。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不对不对，你明明知道的，他这样做，全是为了你，是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他这样对你，也可算是情深义重了，是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我……我……我不知道。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你怎会不知道呢？我问你，连城璧会不会为了你将他的朋友杀死？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "不……不会。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "由此可见，他对你实在比连城璧还好，是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你究竟是不是人？为什么要如此折磨我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风已渐渐大了，若是脱光了衣服，一定会着凉的……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一个人要活着固然很困难，但有时想死却更不容易，是不是？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那么，我问你的话，你现在愿意回答了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我知道你是个很聪明的人，绝不会再做这种笨事的，是不是？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "人家若是对你很好，你是不是应该报答他？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那么，你想你应该如何报答他呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我一定会报答他的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "女人想报答男人，通常只有一个法子，你也是女人，这法子你总该懂得。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你一定懂的，很好……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你既然对她这么好，可愿意娶她做老婆么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "愿意就愿意，不愿意就不愿意，这有什么好紧张的？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "可是……沈姑娘……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你怕她不愿意？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你真是个呆子，她既已答应报答你了，又怎会不愿意？何况，生米若是煮成熟饭，不愿意也得愿意了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "常言道：打铁趁热。只要你点点头，我就替你们作主，让你们就在这里成亲。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "这……这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "这里有什么不好？这么好的地方，不但可以做洞房，还可以做坟墓，就全看你的意思如何了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我愿意，只要公子作主，无论要我做什么，我都愿意。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "这就对了，我现在就去替你们准备洞房花烛，你要好好的看着新娘子，她只有一根舌头，若被她自己咬断了，等会儿你咬什么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是你们的龙凤花烛。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "那就是你们的洞房，你们进洞房的时候，我还可以在外面替你们把风，只望你们这对新人进了房，莫要把我这媒人抛过墙就好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公子……我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你虽然对我不起，我反而替你作媒，找了这么样一个如花似玉的新娘子，你还有什么不满意的？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "可是……以后……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "以后就是你们两个人的事，难道还要我教你么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公子难道真的已饶了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "若不饶你，我何不一刀将你宰了，何必还要费这么大的事？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "多谢公子。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "只不过……有件事你却得多加注意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公子请吩咐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你们两位都是大大有名的人，这婚事不久想必就会传遍江湖，若是被连城璧知道……他只怕就不会像我这么样好说话了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "所以我劝你，成亲之后，赶快找个地方躲起来，最好一辈子再也莫要见人，连城璧的朋友不少，耳目一向灵通得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "还有，你还得小心你这位新娘子，千万莫要让她跑了，半夜睡着的时候也得多加小心，否则她说不定会给你一刀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "不过我还可以教你个法子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公……公子请指教。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你若对新娘子不放心，不妨先废掉她的武功，再锁上她的腿，若能不给她衣服穿，就更保险了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "一个女人若是没有衣眼穿，哪里也去不了的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "春宵一刻值千金，两位还是快入洞房吧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今宵良辰美景，花红叶绿柳成荫，他日……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧十一郎？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "好好的站着，不要动，也不要回头。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你放心，我一向最听话了，你叫我不动，我就不动。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "柳家的大少爷，你也过来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "这位小公子，你认得吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "认……认得。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "其实你该叫她小姑娘才是。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "小姑娘？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你难道看不出她是个女的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你看她长得比那位连夫人怎样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "差……差不多。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "好色的人，毕竟还是有眼光。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你看这位柳家的大少爷长得怎样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "年少英俊，又是名家之子，谁能嫁给他可真是福气。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你愿意嫁给他吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我愿意极了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "既是如此，我就替你们作主，让你们在这里成亲吧，反正洞房花烛，都是现成的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 635
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "柳家的大少爷，你愿意吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "speaker_name": "柳永南",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "你用不着害怕，这位新娘子虽凶些，但你只要先废掉她的武功，再剥光她的衣服，她也凶不起来了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我若能嫁给柳公子，就算变成残废，心里也是欢喜的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 651
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "好人，还不快抱我进洞房，我已等不及了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 655
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_liu_yong_nan",
      "text": "小心！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧十一郎，你用不着替我作媒，将来我想嫁人的时候，一定要嫁给你，我早就看上你了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 673
    }
